   * -->
   *
   * This API is the recommended way to construct injectors in performance-sensitive parts.
   *
   * ### Example ([live demo](http://plnkr.co/edit/VhyfjN?p=preview))
   *
   * ```typescript
   * class ParentProvider {}
   * class ChildProvider {}
